# Mobile Sticky Navigation Behavior Investigation

## Checklist
- [ ] Set browser viewport to mobile size (390x844).
- [ ] Navigate to `http://localhost:3000/aulas/portugues/concordancia`.
- [ ] Verify if the sidebar is visible initially.
- [ ] Scroll down slowly until `StickyModuleNav` pins.
- [ ] Check if the sidebar slides out and the content takes full viewport width.
- [ ] Open the browser console and check for `[sidebar-debug]` logs.
- [ ] Scroll back up to the top and check if the sidebar slides back in.
- [ ] Verify if the sticky nav is full-width (pixel perfect).
- [ ] Check if navigation arrows (left/right) are visible in the sticky nav.
- [ ] Check for other console errors.

